    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A) Opuntia megapotamica (orange flowers). B) Parodia arnostiana (yellow flowers). C) P. herteri (pink flowers). D) P. linkii (yellow flower). E) P. mammulosa (yellow flower). F) P. nothorauschii. G) P. ottonis(flores yellow flower). H) P. ritteriana(yellow flower). I) P. tenuycilindrica. J) Wigginsiasellowii (yellow flower). K) W. langsdorffii (pale-yellow flower). L) W. turbinata (yellow flower). Pictures by A. S. Oliveira." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6415615/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

